==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: tiānshí dìlì rénhé

===Etymology===
Literally: at the right time,in the right place with the right people

===Idiom===
'''[[天时]][[地利]][[人和]]'''
# conditions required for success; knock on wood; if everything goes according to plan; with a little luck; everything goes right
#: '''''天时地利人和'''[[加]][[努力]][[女排]][[的]][[这]][[枚]][[金牌]][[命中]][[注定]]''
#: '''''With a little luck''' and some hard work, the women's volleyball team will be the shoe-in for a gold medal.''

===Alternate forms===
[[天時地利人和]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

